Vidalia onions with coded stickers. That's one of the lessons I
learned during my first encounter with a Kroger U-Scan at the
chain's Monroe Drive store. Our retail reporter confronts her first
U-Scan machine and lives to tell about it. (DeGross, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution).
