   KOREA-EUPHORIA (Hong Kong) _ The startling success of the
North-South Korea summit has much of Asia in euphoria, with
millions glued to their TV sets as people on both sides of the
divided peninsula cheered the two leaders. By Indira A.R.
Lakshmanan. 1200 words.
