   SYRIA-ASSAD (Qordaha, Syria) _ In the remote mountainous
homeland of Hafez Assad _ as well as the site of his deadliest
crackdown _ it's difficult to assess whether the tiny minority
Alewite community will be able to continue its improbable hold on
power. By Charles M. Sennott.
