   WITH
</P>
<P>
   BAPTISTS-COLUMN _ Commentary on the Southern Baptist convention.
(Gushee, Palm Beach Post). 14.
</P>
<P>
   PASTOR-GOINGHOME _ After 50 years of distinguished ministry, the
Rev. D.D. Chestang, pastor of Mount Carmel Missionary Baptist
Church, is going home. The energetic Alabama preacher, who has been
a spiritual divining rod for scores of faithful throughout southern
Ohio, will deliver his farewell sermon June 25 in the sanctuary of
his Jefferson Twp. church. (Dayton Daily News). 21. WITH PHOTO.
</P>
