<P>
   DNC-BAILOUT _ (Los Angeles) A formal request for $4 million in
city funds was presented to the Los Angeles City Council on Friday
to help bail out the committee paying for the Democratic National
Convention in August. Council President John Ferraro introduced the
proposal scheduled for consideration next Tuesday, saying it is
important for the city to present a good image. By Rick Orlov.
