   A Boston Globe article about the AT&AMP;T-MediaOne Group merger
inaccurately characterized the status of AT&AMP;T's efforts to acquire
Charter Communications cable franchises in 53 Worcester, Mass.-area
communities. AT&AMP;T and Charter are continuing negotiations, but AT&AMP;T
