   BBA-SHAUGHNESSY-COLUMN (Boston) _ Legions of Red Sox fans don't
want Sammy Sosa. Afterall, the bum has only knocked in 299 runs in
years and hasn't hit over 63 homers since 1998. By Dan Shaughnessy.
850 words.
</P>
