<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-06-16 22:13 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6626 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r s BC-BKC-KAPONO-LADN     06-16 0395
